*** Keywords ****
Fibonacci List
    [Arguments]    ${n}
    @{fib}    Create List
    Run Keyword If    ${n} > 0    Append To List    ${fib}    ${0}    ${1}
    : FOR    ${i}    IN RANGE    2    ${n} + 1
    \     ${n_2}=    Get From List    ${fib}    ${i-2}
    \     ${n_1}=    Get From List    ${fib}    ${i-1}
    \     ${n_0}=    Evaluate    ${n_1} + ${n_2}
    \     Append To List    ${fib}    ${n_0}
    ${fib}=    Get Slice From List    ${fib}    1
    [Return]    ${fib}